name: DingDong-Afuntakeofthedoorbelltrick
0:
”Alexa, open ding dong”
”Alexa, play ding dong”
”Ring the doorbell”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: ding dong
des:
This is a recreation of the prank played for generations. Join Alexa on an adventure of pressing a neighbors doorbell and see what reaction you get. Try it again and again to see how many times you can get away with it.

If you have an Echo button, use it rather than say "Ring the Doorbell".
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
